# X Strike Force’s documentation

*The “X Strike Force” takes care of packaging X.Org for Debian.*

These documents are shipped in the
[xserver-xorg](http://packages.debian.org/xserver-xorg&exact=1)
metapackage (under `/usr/share/doc/xorg`), starting with `wheezy`.


